:"2023-02-21T01:56:14.226Z","cooked":"<p>If you are looking to contribute you could try making a absolute encoder module for YAGSL by extending <code>SwerveAbsoluteEncoder</code> and adding it where necessary. The code works very well with Neo’s and CANCoders right now so if you can make that drop in replacement it should work just fine.</p>
<p>(Full disclosure I am the developer of it and have been wanting to support this configuration but don’t have the hardware)</p>
